HEADWORD: Modicum
<hw>Mod"i*cum</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., fr.
<ets>modicus</ets> moderate, fr. <ets>modus</ets>. See
<er>Mode</er>.]</ety> <def>A little; a small quantity; a measured
